'''Christian Homer "Chris" Mulkey Jr.''' portrayed [[Bud Schultz]] in the ''[[Agent Carter (TV series)|Agent Carter]]'' episode ''[[Smoke & Mirrors]]''.

==Trivia==
*Chris Mulkey is one of the many actors to portray characters for both [[Marvel Television]] and {{WPS|DC_Comics#DC_Entertainment|DC Entertainment}}. He voiced Walter Shriev/Shriek in ''{{WPS|Batman Beyond}}''.

